T}
.TE
.PP
When the exception happens, use getLastErrMsg() to get the error message or use
getLastError() to get the error code.
For more details, refer to Troubleshooting.
.SH VERSION
.PP
v1.10 and above
.SH EXAMPLES
.IP \[bu] 2
Get the index named ageIndex from the sample.employee collection.
.PP
\f[C]>\ db.sample.employee.getIndex(\ "ageIndex"\ )\f[]
